  Anglo American Plc ’s  Kumba Iron Ore
Ltd . was given a written undertaking by  South Africa ’s state
attorney saying the Department of Mineral Resources won’t award
a mining right at Sishen mine to Imperial Crown Trading 289 Ltd.
before the completion of a related court hearing.  Kumba commented in an e-mailed reply to a query today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
